                "Mild interference with usual ADLs/work, recreation/community activities, and/or personal relationships due to the entitled condition(s).",
                "Able to perform domestic activities independently but with greater effort; or able to work in usual occupation with difficulty and/or minor workplace modifications or task restructuring.",
                "Able to drive/use public transport independently; may require adaptations or more frequent breaks.",
                "Mild reduction in type/frequency/quality of recreational and community activities; activities remain satisfying with routine adjustments.",
                "Mild reduction in scope/frequency/quality of usual social/interpersonal relationships; may avoid large gatherings; some family/social responsibilities limited by the entitled condition(s)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": "L2",
              "label": "Level 2",
              "criteria": [
                "Moderate interference with ADLs/work, recreation/community activities, and/or personal relationships due to the entitled condition(s).",
                "Domestic activities require assistance/special adaptations; OR unable to work full time in normal occupation or had to change occupation/hours because of the entitled condition(s).",
                "Unable to drive but can travel using public or private transportation with assistance and/or vehicular adaptations.",
                "Moderate reduction in recreational/community activities; requires assistance and structured changes to continue participation.",
                "Moderate reduction in social/interpersonal relationships; relationships primarily with immediate family/close friends; most usual family responsibilities not carried out and/or distress with usual social activities."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": "L3",
              "label": "Level 3",
              "criteria": [
                "Extreme interference with ADLs/work, recreation/community activities, and/or personal relationships due to the entitled condition(s).",
                "Not able to complete most domestic activities even with assistance/adaptations; OR unable to work due to the entitled condition(s).",
                "Not able to use public or private transportation; dependent on transportation for the disabled.",
                "Extreme limitation in recreational/community activities; unable to take part in usual or alternate activities.",
